content:
Map Skills to Learning Content for Agent Engagement

Associate skills with custom enablement site (myTrailhead) learning modules so agents earn skills upon module completion.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience. It's available in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited Editions.

Open Setup | Workforce Engagement | Skills | Skills & Learning.
Click New Match.
Search for a skill.
Click Next.
Search for the enablement site module you'd like to match to this skill, and click to add it.
Check the box to Approve Automatically. After an agent completes the learning module, they'll automatically earn the skill.
Save your changes.
title: Configuring Skills and Learning for Agent Engagement in Service Cloud
